OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FITV reporter Sarah Saunders visited
OL,8,Fthe Hartley House care home in
OL,9,FCranbrook, which has been struggling
OL,10,Fwithout water for the past five days.
OL,12,FAt Hartley House care home in
OL,13,FCranbrook, they've been trying to cope
OL,14,Fwithout water for the past FIVE days.
OL,16,FIt's not been easy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
