FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,F"This is what we are using to wash our
OL,8,Fresidents," says manager Rachel Dadwa-
OL,9,FAs, pointing to a mountain of two
OL,10,Flitre bottles of water, "It's what we
OL,11,Fuse to give them a shower, and to keep
OL,12,Fboth them and staff hydrated."
OL,14,FThey look after more than 50 older
OL,15,Fpeople here, many of them with
OL,16,Fdementia.
OL,18,FIt's a huge pressure on staff to keep
OL,19,Fresidents hydrated, clean and healthy
OL,20,Fin these conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,F"We know we are dealing with
OL,8,Fvulnerable people," says Rachel. "But
OL,9,Fwhat can we do? Maybe we could be
OL,10,Fprovided with a tank, for an emergency
OL,11,Flike this."
OL,13,FOther staff members, Laura Wood and
OL,14,FTracey Blake, told us a lot of their
OL,15,Fresidents have dementia, and don't
OL,16,Funderstand the change in their
OL,17,Froutine. "You really don't want to be
OL,18,Fwashing them with wet wipes, and dry
OL,19,Fwipes, said Tracey. "It's not fair on
OL,20,Fthem."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
