OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FIn the kitchen, chef Alexio is having
OL,8,Fto boil bottled water in order to
OL,9,Fclean and cook food, and wash up
OL,10,Fafterwards.
OL,12,F"It's extremely difficult," he says.
OL,13,F"I'm cooking for around 70 residents
OL,14,Fand staff, and having to do it for
OL,15,Fevery meal, day after day."
OL,17,FSouth East Water says more than 600
OL,18,Fcustomers are still without water in
OL,19,Fthe Wraik Hill area of Kent. Thousands
OL,20,Fof others continue to experience low
OL,21,Fpressure and intermittent service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
