PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FIn a statement the company said today:
OL,8,F"Although our network is continuing to
OL,9,Frecover, levels of drinking water in
OL,10,Four storage tanks are still low and we
OL,11,Fare asking customers to use water for
OL,12,Fessential purposes only."
OL,14,FAnd it is continuing to offer bottled
OL,15,Fwater stations - and use tankers to
OL,16,Fsupport the network and aid recovery.
OL,18,FAt the height of this week's water
OL,19,Fsupply issues, more than 18,000 people
OL,20,Fin Kent and Sussex have been affected.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
