OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FDuring a heatwave when temperatures
OL,8,Freached 30 C and above during
OL,9,Fconsistent days, South East Water
OL,10,Fcustomers have had to reply on bottled
OL,11,Fsupplies.
OL,13,FYesterday the Ashford MP, Sojan
OL,14,FJoseph, criticised South East Water
OL,15,Ffor what he says are 'repeated
OL,16,Ffailures'.
OL,26,@pD@LOX
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
