PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780330269
OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FHe said: "I have completely lost faith
OL,8,Fin South East Water ` they have
OL,9,Frepeatedly failed to improve standards
OL,10,Ffor customers in my constituency and
OL,11,Facross Kent.
OL,13,FSouth East Water have not invested in
OL,14,Fthe necessary infrastructure and, as a
OL,15,Fresult, have failed to ensure they do
OL,16,Fnot face shortages at times of high
OL,17,Fdemand ` this time just after a couple
OL,18,Fof days of warm weather.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
