OL,3,CCare home forced to clean residents
OL,4,Cwith wet wipes after five days without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FI completely understand the
OL,8,Ffrustration of residents. I have
OL,9,Fwritten to DEFRA to ask the Secretary
OL,10,Fof State to take action and have been
OL,11,Fmaintaining contact with South East
OL,12,FWater on behalf of my constituents to
OL,13,Fstay on top of the detail.
